{"id": "1237409415536181279", "channel_id": "1234861134616465549", "type": 0, "author_id": "1073914607741177866", "author_name": "scholar_2", "author_bot": false, "content": "新版加强方式：\n評價是可以做强效了，兩人都能吃到强效收益\n算了一下，做70强效的話\n現在70級大招45點薔薇56點，加强之後是大招75點薔薇74點\n進門基礎128，道中一般吃1個是140基礎，boss前兩波吃3個分別是167和200，最後一波吃4-5個是256-270\n跟現在（我的是50强效出門67點基礎）比起來道中等於大招多70點力量，boss多100-200點力量，非常猛", "timestamp": "2024-05-07T14:23:14.619000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-05-07T14:26:56.115000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1237409415339180102", "filename": "166V7MYDPIIQBNC51_JO.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 63325, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1234861134616465549/1237409415339180102/166V7MYDPIIQBNC51_JO.png?ex=69cbd8d2&is=69ca8752&hm=0543bab719926a1eb5eeabf2f494c254c9cbc0011b2ffd037f3190499bb46a11&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1234861134616465549", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "高攻刺客二人组——红花24双C队伍", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1227516925479747584", "1174179734373019748"]}
